\v 13 Ez…® k…® God ingarizir gumaziba ko biziba bar men ighiam barasi, bizir overiam…®n itiba ko nguazim…®n itiba ko nguazim…®n apengan itiba ko ongarim…®n itiba. K…® orazi da kamagh m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúGumazir uan atrivir dabirabim gapiaghirim, ko sipsip…®n nguzim uaghan, e zurazurara aning m…®nab…®v…®ra ikiam.
\q1 Egh aning…®n ziar ekiamning f…®va, aning bagh bar akongegh egh aning…®n gavgavir ekiam…®n apengan ik…® zurara mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\b
\m 
\v 14 Ez…® 4 plan bizir angamra itiba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir dapaniba tevir akuriba ap…®righa aning…®n ziamning fe.
\c 6
\s1 Sipsip…®n Nguzim ak…®nafarim…®n kandel…®n grisba adangi
\p 
\v 1 K…® Sipsip…®n Nguzim…®n gari, a 7 plan kandel…®n gris…®n itir ak…®nafarir kam…®n suiragha egha a kandel gris…®n namba wan adangi. Ez…® k…® orazi, 4 plan bizir angamra itir kabar mav kamagh…®n m…®gei, ez…® an tiarim mati ararim dagaravagha, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® iz…®!‚Äù
\v 2 Ez…® k…® ua gara egha hoziar ghurghurir mam…®n gari, gumazim barirpim…®n suiragha a gapera. Me atrivim…®n dapanir asuar mam a gan…®ngi, ez…® a m…®dorozim gamua uan apanim ab…®raz…® mogh…®n zui, egha m…®dorozir av…®ribagh amua uan apaniba ab…®ra ghuav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® Sipsip…®n Nguzim ak…®nafarim…®n kandel…®n gris…®n namba 2 adangi, ez…® k…® orazi, bizir angamra itir namba 2 kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® iz…®!‚Äù
\v 4 Ez…® hoziar igharazim azenan izi, an aghefe. Me gavgavim hoziar kam gaperazir gumazim gan…®ngi, kar gavgavir nguazim…®n gumazamizibar dughiar aghuim a g…®vamim, eght…® gumaziba igharaz daraziv soght…®ma me ar…®m…®ghiram. Ez…® me m…®dorozir sabar ekiar mam ingangarir kam damuasava a gan…®ngi.
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® sipsip…®n nguzim ak…®nafarim…®n kandel…®n gris…®n namba 3 adangi, ez…® k…® orazi bizir angamra itir namba 3 kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® iz…®!‚Äù Ez…® k…® ua gara, egha hoziar p…®zim…®n gari. Ez…® gumazir a gaperaghav itim a skel…®n mam uan dafarim…®n an suira.
\v 6 Ez…® k…® orazi, mati gumazim…®n tiarim bizir angamra itir 4 plan kabar tong…®n m…®g…®a, egha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…® uan ingangarim damut…®, eght…® dagheba bar otevegham. Kamagh…®n, gumazim dughiar vam…®ran ivezim inigh, a wit…®n m…®ner muziarir vam…®ra o balin m…®ner muziarir 3 plara givezam. Egh ia oliv…®n temeba ko wain…®n beniba gas…®ghas…®ghan mark…®, eght…® oliv…®n borem ko wain ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Sipsip…®n Nguzim ak…®nafarim…®n kandel…®n gris…®n namba 4 adangiz…®ma, k…® orazi bizir angamra itir namba 4 kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® iz…®!‚Äù
\v 8 Ez…® k…® ua gara hoziar iangurim…®n gari. Ez…® gumazir a gaperazim, an ziam Ovevem. Ez…® Nguibar Gumaziba Ovia Ghua Itim, an Ovevem…®n g…®rara izi. God gavgavim kamagh…®n aning gan…®ngi, aning nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba 4 plan okuruabar me tuiragh, egh okuruar kabar aven aning okuruar vam…®ra, aning a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. Aning gumazamiziba m…®dorozir sabam…®n me m…®sueght…®, me ar…®m…®ghiram, eght…® aning m…®tiriar ekiam damight…® an otoght…® me ar…®m…®ghiram, eght…® aning ar…®mariar ekiabar amut…® da otiv me damut…® me ar…®m…®ghiram, eght…® aning ruarim…®n itir as…®zir atiaba amangt…® da mang…® me m…®soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiram.
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Sipsip…®n Nguzim ak…®nafarim…®n kandel…®n gris…®n namba 5 adangiz…®ma, k…® gari, gumazamizir ovengezibar duaba God…®n ofa gamir danganim apengan iti. Gumazamizir kaba faragha God…®n akam…®n suiragha gavgavigha, egha akar kam akuni, ez…® bizir kam…®n apaniba me m…®soghez…® me ariagh…®re.
\v 10 Duar kaba dia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGavgaviba bar itir Ekiam, n…® arazir kuraba bar dar saghon ikia egha bar zue! Ez…® n…®n akar d…®k…®r…®ziba da guizbang…®ra otifi! E n…® m…®zua iti, n…® zuam…®ra nguazim…®n itir gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®gh…®va, egh en ghuzim…®n ivezim ikarvagh!‚Äù
\v 11 Egha me gumazamizir kaba vaghvagha korotiar ghurghurir ruariba me gan…®ngi, egha kamagh me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa tong orark…®va avughs…® ik…®. Apaniba ian adarazi ko ia ko ingari darazi m…®sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregham, mati me ia m…®soghez…® mok…®n. God, gumazamizir apaniba me m…®sueght…® ar…®m…®ghiramibar namba g…®fogha g…®fa, eght…® apaniba gumazamizir kabav sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghireght…®, God ian ghuzim…®n ivezim ikarvagham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Sipsip…®n Nguzim ak…®nafarim…®n kandel…®n gris…®n namba 6 adangiz…®ma, ez…® k…® ua gari, m…®k…®mk…®zir dafam nguazim…®n oto. Ez…® aruem isiragha gari puvat…®z…®, overiam ko nguazim m…®tatangi. Ez…® iakinim bar aghevegha ghuzim…®n m…®n gari.
\v 13 Ez…® p…®n itir m…®koveziba asiaghira nguazim giri, mati am…®nim figh…®n temem givai, ez…® figh…®n ov…®zir t…®ghar aniamiba suaghiri.
\v 14 Overiam mati, ak…®nafarir bar dafam me a righa anet…®z…® mogh…®n, a uan danganim ataki. Ez…® m…®ghs…®aba ko arighat…®ziba bar uan danganiba ategha, egha s…®vagha ghue.
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® nguazim…®n atriviba ko gumazir ziaba itiba ko m…®dorozir gumazir dapaniba ko dag…®aba itir gumaziba ko gumazir gavgaviba ko pura ingangarir gumazir k…®niba ko gumazir f…®riaghreziba, me bar mogh…®ra ghua marazi dag…®ar toribar aven mongez…® marazi m…®ghs…®abar itir dag…®ar ekiabar g…®rak…®rang…®n monge.
\v 16 Egha me m…®ghs…®aba ko dag…®ar ekiaba kamagh…®n dar dei, ‚ÄúIa e avaragh, egh gumazir atrivir dabirabim gaperaghav itim…®n guam…®n e modogh, egh ia uaghan Sipsip…®n Nguzim…®n an…®ngagharim…®n e modogh!
\v 17 E fo, aning…®n an…®ngagharim…®n dughiar ekiam dat…®r…®gh…®n otoz…® aning gumazamizibar arazir kuraba ikarvaghasa. Eght…® gumazitam aning…®n an…®ngagharim iriagh, angamra ikian kogham!‚Äù
\c 7
\s1 144,000 plan Israel…®n gumazamiziba, God me ginabazir osizirim, enselba me gar…®si
\p 
\v 1 Bizir kaba g…®vaz…®ma, ez…® k…® gari, ensel…®n 4 pla nguazim…®n 4 plan ap…®nibar tuivighav iti. Me nguazim…®n 4 plan am…®nibar tuaviba ap…®ri, eght…® am…®nim mang…® ongarim ko nguazim ko temeba bar dagh ivangan kogham.
\v 2 Ez…® k…® ensel…®n igharazim…®n gari, an aruem anadi nagh…®n ikeghav anadi. A God…®n zurazurara itim…®n inabazir osizirim an iti, egha a ensel…®n 4 plan God ongarim ko nguazim gas…®ghas…®ghamin gavgavim an…®ngiziba pamten men dei.
\v 3 A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa zuam…®ra nguazim ko ongarim ko temebagh as…®ghas…®ghan mark…®. God uan ingangarir gumazibagh inabas. E faragh uan God…®n ingangarir gumaziba, inabazir osizirim e men guabar an osirigh g…®vaght…®, ia g…®n bizibagh as…®ghas…®gh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® k…® orazi, me gumazamizir inabazir osizirim isibar d…®bobonim d…®bori. Me 144,000 plan gumazamiziba, inabazir osizirim me gar…®si, me Israel…®n kantrin aven itir 12 plan anababa, vaghvagha men varazira, osizirim ini.\f + \ft (7:4) Osizirir kamnagh ‚ÄúIsrael…®n kantrin aven itir 12 plan anababar‚Äù gun m…®gei. E Aruamu e ghaze, anabam, kar amebam o amizim…®n ghuzim. Ez…® Israelba me ghaze, anabam, kar afeziam…®n ghuzim, egha me afeziabar g…®n zui.\f*
\b
\q1 
\v 5 Ez…® 12,000 plan Judan anabam…®n aven itir darasi,
\q2 me inabazir osizirim ini,
\q1 ez…® 12,000 plan Ruben…®n anabam…®n adarasi,
\q1 ez…® 12,000 plan Gat…®n anabam…®n adarasi,
\q1 
\v 6 ez…® 12,000 plan Aser…®n anabam…®n adarasi,
\q1 ez…® 12,000 plan Natalin anabam…®n adarasi,
\q1 ez…® 12,000 plan Manasen anabam…®n adarasi,
\q1 
\v 7 ez…® 12,000 plan Simeon…®n anabam…®n adarasi,
\q1 ez…® 12,000 plan Livain anabam…®n adarasi,
\q1 ez…® 12,000 plan Isakar…®n anabam…®n adarasi,
\q1 
\v 8 ez…® 12,000 plan Sebulun…®n anabam…®n adarasi,
\q1 ez…® 12,000 plan Josep…®n anabam…®n adarasi,
\q1 ez…® 12,000 plan Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarasi.
\b
\m Gumazamizir kaba me God me ginabazir osizirim ini.
\s1 Gumazamizir bar av…®rim God…®n ziam fe
\p 
\v 9 Egha k…® g…®n ua gari, gumazamizir av…®rim uari akuvagha iti. Gumazitam men av…®rim mengan iburagham. Gumazamizir kaba, me kantriba bar ko anababa bar ko m…®karzir igharagha gariba bar ko nguibabar akaba bar dar gumazamiziba, men marazira izegha iti. Me atrivir dabirabim ko Sipsip…®n Nguzim…®n guam…®n tuivighav iti. Me korotiar ghurghurir ruariba aghui, egha uan agharibar okavir aghuabar suiki.
\v 10 Me pamten kamagh…®n dei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúEn God…®n uan atrivir dabirabim gaperazim,
\q2 ko Sipsip…®n Nguzim, aningra en akuragha en apanim ab…®ra.
\q3 Ez…® e aning…®n ziamning fe.‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® enselba bar ikia, atrivir dabirabim ko 4 plan bizir angamra itiba ko gumazir dapaniba, me me okarigha tuivighav iti. Egha atrivir dabirabim…®n garava tevir akuriba ap…®ra egha uan guaba nguazim m…®suegha, egha God…®n ziam fe.
\v 12 Me kamagh…®n m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra!
\q2 E uan God ziar ekiam a dan…®ng, egh a bagh bar akongegham,
\q3 egh kamagh m…®k…®m suam, an fofozim bar p…®n iti.
\q1 Egh a m…®nab…®va, egh an ziam fam.
\q2 A gavgavir ekiam iti, eght…® e an gavgavim…®n apengan ikiam.
\q3 Dughiabar zurara bizir kaba bar mogh…®rama God…®n biziba.
\q1 Bar guizbang…®ra!‚Äù
\s1 Krais…®n adarasi, men os…®mt…®zim g…®fa
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® gumazir dapanibar mav kamagh nan azara, ‚ÄúGumazamizir korotiar ruarir ghurghuriba aghuizir kaba, me taia? Me managh…®ra ikegha ize?‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® k…® an akam kamagh a ikara, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, n…® uab…® fo.‚Äù Ez…® a kamagh na m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúGumazamizir kaba me uan apanibar dafaribar os…®mt…®ziba ko m…®zazir ekiaba ini.
\q2 Ez…® os…®mt…®zir dughiam dat…®r…®gh…®n g…®fa.
\q1 Ez…® me uan korotiaba Sipsip…®n Nguzim…®n ghuzim…®n da ruegha,
\q2 dagh amiz…®, da ghurghuri.
\q1 
\v 15 Kamagh…®n amiz…® me atrivir dabirabim…®n guam…®n tuifi.
\q2 Egha d…®magariba ko aruebar an d…®penim…®n ikia egha an ingangarim gami.
\q1 Ez…® God…®n atrivir dabirabir kam gaperaghav itim, a uab…® me ko ik…® egh me geghuvam.
\q2 
\v 16 Eght…® m…®tiriaba ua men aghan kogham, eght…® kuariba ua men p…®ran kogham.
\q1 Eght…® aruer ar…®zir m…®karziba puv…®ra dagh aboim, ua men m…®karzibar isian kogham.
\q2 
\v 17 Sipsip…®n Nguzim atrivir dabirabim…®n tong…®ra ikia, egha me geghufi.
\q1 Egha a me inigh nguazim…®n aven ivemarir d…®par atuir danganim…®n mangam, kar d…®par ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dim.
\q2 Egh God men temeriba bar men damazibar da dizight…® da m…®sigam, eght…® me uam azian kogham.‚Äù
\c 8
\s1 Sipsip…®n Nguzim ak…®nafarir r…®ghizim…®n kandel…®n gris…®n abuananam adangi
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Sipsip…®n Nguzim ak…®nafarim…®n itir kandel…®n gris…®n namba 7 adangi, ez…® God…®n Nguibam…®n bizitam bar mozorozir pu, ez…® m…®g…®r…®g…®atam otivir puvat…®gha, ghua mong dughiar ruarim kamagh…®n tu.
\v 2 Ez…® g…®n k…® 7 plan ensel…®n gari, me God…®n guam…®n tuifi, egha 7 pla s…®ghaba ini.
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® ensel…®n igharazim iza ofa gamir danganim borogh…®n tughav iti. A gol…®n m…®ner mam…®n suira, m…®ner kam, me an aven paura tuaz…® a isia m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim oto. Ez…® me pauran av…®rir maba a gan…®ngi, eght…® a God…®n gumazamizibar azangs…®zibar sara isafuragh, egh atrivir dabirabim…®n guam…®n mang…®va gol…®n ofa gamir danganim…®n God bagh ofa damuam.
\v 4 Ez…® pauran isir m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim ko God…®n gumazamizibar azangs…®ziba, da uari inigha ensel…®n God…®n damazim…®n tughav itir kam…®n dafarim ategha ghuavanadi.
\v 5 Ez…® ensel m…®ner m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim itim suiragha ghua ofa gamir danganim…®n ghua avim inigha m…®nem garu, egha m…®nem akuniz…®ma a nguazim gir…®. An anekunigha g…®vaz…®ma, arariba dagarvazima maburan n…®g…®nim oto, ez…® overiam…®n on…®mariba taghtagha tintinibar zui, ez…® m…®k…®mk…®zim oto.
\s1 Ensel…®n 4 pla s…®ghabagh ivi
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® ensel…®n 7 plan, s…®ghar 7 plan suighizir kaba, me dagh iviasava ami.
\p 
\v 7 Namba 1 ensel uan s…®gham givi, ez…® amozir of…®zir ekiar dag…®abar m…®n gariba ko avim, aning ghuzim sara isafuragha nguazim giri. Ez…® me nguazim ko temeba 3 plan okuruaba da tuira, dar okuruar mam avim bar an isi. Ez…® bizir nguazim…®n aghuiba bar, da uaghan avim a dar isi.
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® namba 2 ensel uan s…®gham givi, ez…® me, bizir mam mati m…®ghs…®ar ekiam…®n m…®n avim an isima, me anekuniz…® a ghua ongarim giraghu. Ez…® ongarim 3 plan okuruaba uab…® tuiraz…®, ez…® ongarim…®n okuruar mam ghuzim…®n oto.
\v 9 Bizir ongarim…®n angamra itiba, da uaghan me okuruar 3 plan da tuira, ez…® dar okuruar kabar mam, da bar ariagh…®re. Ez…® kuriba uaghan, me okuruar 3 plan da tuira, ez…® kurir okuruar kabar mam, bar mogh…®ra ikufi.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® namba 3 ensel uan s…®gham givi, ez…® m…®kovezir ekiar mam adenim…®n m…®n puv…®ra isia, overiam ategha ir…®. Ez…® me faner d…®paba okuruar 3 plan da tuira, ez…® m…®kovezir kam d…®par okuruar kabar mam gira, egha uaghan d…®par atuibagh ir…®.
\v 11 M…®kovezir kam…®n ziam kamak…®n, Marasin…®n Bar Puv…®ra M…®sozim. A d…®par okuruar kabar mam gir…®z…®, d…®par kaba Marasin…®n Bar Puv…®ra M…®sozim…®n oto. Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba d…®par kam apima a men navibar isiz…® me ariagh…®re.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® ensel…®n namba 4 uan s…®gham givi, ez…® me aruem ko iakinim ko m…®koveziba 3 plan okuruaba da tuira. Egha me aruem…®n okuruar mam gas…®ghas…®gha, egha iakinim…®n okuruar mam gas…®ghas…®gha, egha m…®kovezibar okuruar mam gas…®ghas…®ki. Kamagh…®n amiz…® arueba bar, dughiar mabar aruem isir puvat…®gha m…®tatangi, ez…® d…®magariba bar, d…®magarir maba iakinim ko m…®koveziba isir puvat…®gha angazangariba puvat…®.
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® k…® garima, kuarazir bagar mam overiam…®n p…®n m…®ghagha arui. Ez…® k…® a barazi, a kamagh…®n pamten dia m…®gei, ‚ÄúIavzika! Nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba, Iavzika! Ensel…®n igharazir 3 pla ua uan s…®ghabagh iviam, eght…® os…®mt…®zir bar ekiaba gumazamiziba me bativam. Iavzika!‚Äù
\c 9
\s1 Namba 5 ensel uan s…®gham givi
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® ensel…®n namba 5 uan s…®gham givi, ez…® k…® garima, m…®kovezir mam overiam ategha nguazim gir…®. Ez…® me mozir torir bar konezim…®n akam…®n ki a gan…®ngi.
\v 2 Ez…® m…®kovezir kam, mozir torir bar konezim…®n akam kuiz…®, ez…® m…®gharim torir akam…®n azenan otiva, egha avir bar ekiam…®n m…®gharim…®n m…®n anadi. Egha m…®gharim torir kam…®n anaga aruem ko overiam avaraz…®, aning m…®tatangi.
\v 3 Ez…® odezir bar av…®rim m…®gharir kam ategha zaghira, nguazim tintinibar an zui. God tuighakabar gavgavim…®n m…®n gavgavim dagh an…®ngi, nguazim…®n itir gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®ghamin gavgavim.
\v 4 God odezir kaba kamagh dav gei, ‚ÄúIa zuravariba ko nguazim…®n aghuir biziba ko temer tabagh as…®ghas…®ghan mark…®. Ia, gumazamizir God inabazir osizirim men guabar itir puvat…®ziba, me gas…®ghas…®gh.
\v 5 K…® ian amamangat…®, ia gumazamizir kaba iakinir 5 plara m…®zazir ekiam me dan…®ng. Egh ia me m…®soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiran mark…®.‚Äù Ez…® odezir kaba, m…®zazir da gumazamizibagh an…®diba, tuighakaba ivir m…®zazibar m…®rara ghu.
\v 6 Dughiar kam…®n gumazamiziba ovengs…® tuaviba buriam, egh me ovengan kogham. Me ovengs…® bar ifueght…®, eght…® ovevem men ar…®mangam.
\p 
\v 7 K…® odezir kabar gari, da mati hoziaba m…®dorozim damuasava ami. Dar dapanibar, biziba mati gol…®n dapanir asuabar m…®n dar dapanibar iti. Ez…® dar guaba mati gumazibar guaba.
\v 8 Ez…® dar dapanir ar…®ziba ruarigha, amizibar dapanir ar…®zibar m…®n ruari. Ez…® dar atariba, laion…®n ataribar m…®n, ruarigha bar ghumi.
\v 9 Bizir maba, siot kapabar m…®n gara, dar evariba ave. Ez…® dar av…®ziba t…®ngagha mati hoziaba karis…®n av…®riba kurvagha m…®dorozim bagha ivemara zui mogh…®n t…®ngazi.
\v 10 Odezir kaba tuighakabar ipebar m…®n ipeba iti, ez…® atarir marasin…®n m…®zazir kuraba iziba, dar ipebar iti. Ez…® m…®zazir gavgavir gumazamiziba 5 plan iak…®nibar me dan…®ngamim, a dar ipebar iti.
\v 11 Egha da atrivir mam iti, a dar gari. Atrivir kam, a mozir torir bar konezim…®n garir ensel. Hibrun akam…®n me ensel…®n kam…®n ziam d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúAbadon.‚Äù Ez…® Grigh…®n akam…®n me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄúApoliyon.‚Äù An m…®ngarim kamak…®n, gumazir biziba bar dagh as…®ghas…®zim.
\p 
\v 12 Iavzika, ia orakigh! Os…®mt…®zir bar ekiar faragh zuim, a g…®fa. Ez…® os…®mt…®zir ekiar pumuning ikiav…®ra iti, aning t…®ghar otivam.
\s1 Ensel…®n namba 6 uan s…®gham givi
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® ensel…®n namba 6 uan s…®gham givi, ez…® k…® gumazir mam…®n tiarim barasi, A, God…®n guam…®n itir gol…®n ofa gamir danganir mam…®n iti, danganir kam, a m…®kebar 4 pla iti, ez…® da vaghvagha komba iti. Tiarir k…® orazir kam, a kom…®n 4 plan tong…®n otivima, k…® a barasi.
\v 14 A namba 6 ensel…®n s…®gham…®n suirazim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúEnsel…®n 4 plan Yufretis…®n faner ekiam…®n kalabus…®n itiba, n…® me ateght…® me mang…®.‚Äù
\v 15 Ez…® a 4 plan ensel…®n kaba ataki, eght…® me 3 plan okuruabar gumazamiziba tuiragham, egh okuruatam bar a m…®sueght…® an ar…®m…®ghiregham. God faragha ghaze, auan kam ko aruer kam ko iakinir kam ko azenir kam…®n ensel…®n kaba ingangarir kam damuam. Ez…® ensel…®n kaba kalabus…®n ikia uari ak…®righa ingangarir kam damuasav…®ra dughiar kam…®n m…®zua iti.
\v 16 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir hoziabagh apiaziba, k…® orazima, men d…®bobonim, 200 milien.
\p 
\v 17 Egha k…® irebam…®n m…®n bizim…®n gari, hoziaba ko gumazir hoziabagh apiaziba, men ganganim kamak…®n. Gumaziba siot kapaba aghui, ez…® dar ganganim aghevegha, blu gamigha, iangurungi. Hoziabar dapaniba, laion…®n dapanibar m…®n gari. Ez…® avim ko m…®gharim ko salfan dag…®ar isiba, da hoziabar akabar otivava tintinibar zui.
\v 18 Egha me gumazamiziba 3 plan okuruabar me tuira, ez…® 3 plan bizir bar kuraba, me okuruar mam bar a m…®soghez…®ma an ariagh…®re. Bizir 3 plan kabanagh, da avim ko m…®gharim ko salfan dag…®ar avim, da hoziabar akabar otifi. Bizir 3 plan kabar gavgavim gumazamizir kabagh amima me ariaghiri.
\v 19 Hoziar kabar gavgavim, dar akaba ko ipebar iti. Dar ipeba kuruzibar m…®n gari, egha dapaniba iti. Hoziaba uan ipebar gumazamiziba m…®zazir kuram me gan…®di.
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® gumazamizir igharazir me m…®soghez…®, ariaghrezir puvat…®ziba, me navibagh irazir puvat…®gha egha, ak…®rim ragha marvir guar me uari ingarizibagh asarazir puvat…®. Me aseba ko marvir guaba ataghizir puvat…®. Marvir guar kaba, gumaziba silva ko gol ko bras ko dag…®aba ko temebar dar ingari, da bizibar garir puvat…®gha akaba barazir puvat…®gha aruir puvat…®ziba. Me marvir guabar ziaba fer arazim ataghizir puvat…®.
\v 21 Egha me, gumazir igharazibav sozima me ariaghirir arazim, ko imezibagh amir araziba, ko gumazamiziba tintinibar uari bak…®a uari ko akuir arazim, ko igharaz darazir biziba okeir arazim, me da bagh navibagh iragh arazir kurar kaba ataghraghan aghua.
\c 10
\s1 Ensel ak…®nafarir r…®ghizim Jon gan…®ngiz…® ananepi
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® k…® garima ensel…®n gavgavir igharazir mam God…®n Nguibam ategha izaghiri. A ghuariam korotiam…®n m…®n aneru, ez…® akianir mam an dapanim gis…®n iti. An guam aruem…®n m…®n isi, ez…® an suemning d…®penir ak…®nimning…®n m…®n gara egha avim…®n m…®n isi.
\v 2 Ensel…®n kam ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir muziarim uan dafarim…®n an suira, ez…® ak…®nafarim oneaghr…®gha iti. Egha a uan suer guvim ongarim gasara, egha suer k…®riam nguazim gasara.
\v 3 Egha a bar pamten laion…®n m…®n itiarim akara dia m…®gei. A diagha g…®vaz…®ma, 7 plan arariba dagarvagha egha an akam ikara.
\v 4 Egha 7 plan ararir kaba dagarvegha g…®vaz…®ma, ez…® k…® akar me m…®kemeziba osirasa. Ez…® God…®n Nguibam…®n k…® gumazir mam…®n d…®mdiam barazima, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚Äú7 plan ararir dagarvaghizibar akam, n…® uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n anet…®ght…®ma a ik…®. N…® an osiran mark…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ensel…®n k…® ganizir kam an ongarim ko nguazim…®n tughav ikia, uan agharir guvim overiam…®n p…®n a fe.
\v 6 Egha ghaze, ‚ÄúGod…®n zurara itim…®n ziam…®n k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei. God…®n kam, an overiam ko bizir an itibar ingarigha egha nguazim ko an itir bizibar ingarigha, ongarim ko an itir bizibar ingari. Ez…® k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, dughiam dat…®r…®gh…®n g…®vasava ami. God uam orarkian kogham. Bar puvat…®.
\v 7 Bizir God damuasava amim an akam modoghav iti. Eght…® Ensel…®n namba 7 s…®gham givit…®ma, dughiar kamra bizir modoghav itim guizbang…®ram otogham. Kar, akar aghuir a fom…®ra uan ingangarir gumazibagh an…®ngizim, me an akam inigha izir gumaziba.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® gumazir k…® God…®n Nguibam…®n faragha oraghizim, a ua kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® ensel…®n ongarim ko nguazim…®n tughav itim…®n dafarim…®n ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir oneghav itim inigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® k…® ensel bagha ghua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir muziarir kam na dan…®ngigh.‚Äù Ez…® a kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® a inigh…®va, anerem…®. A n…®n navim…®n aven n…® m…®sogham. Egh n…®n akam…®n an hanin m…®n bar s…®ngigham.‚Äù
\v 10 A m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, k…® ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir muziarim an dafarim…®n a inighava anepi. Ez…® nan akam…®n a hanin m…®n bar s…®ngi. K…® anemegha g…®vaz…®ma, a nan navim…®n aven na m…®sosi.
\v 11 Ez…® me kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ua God da izezir akam…®n gun m…®k…®m. Akar kam…®n, m…®karzir igharagha garir av…®riba ko kantrin av…®riba ko nguibabar akar av…®riba ko atrivir av…®riba, bizir me bativamiba n…® dar me m…®k…®m.‚Äù
\c 11
\s1 God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir pumuning
\p 
\v 1 Egha me aghorir bizibar abarim na gan…®ngi, an aghorir suiagharuim…®n m…®n gari, egha me kamagh na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh God…®n D…®penim ko ofa gamir danganim…®n apan. Egh n…® d…®penir kam…®n God…®n ziam fer gumazamizibar d…®bobonim d…®pon.
\v 2 Egh n…® God…®n D…®penim okarizir danganir d…®vazir ekiam…®n aven itim, an apanan mark…®. God Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba danganir uari akuvir kam me gan…®ngi. Eght…® marazi iz…® Jerusalem d…®k…® mang…® 42 plan iak…®nibar tugham. Kamagh…®n, n…® anetakigh.\f + \ft (11:2) Akar Mogomem 11:2…®n faragha itir akam, n…® Aposelbar Ingangaribar 21:30…®n gan. Akar Mogomem 11:2…®n akar igharazir kam, 42 plan iak…®niba, da 1,260 plan dughiaba, o 3 plan azeniba g…®vaz…®ma uam akuam. Da 42 plan iak…®niba ko magh ghue. N…® Daniel 7:25 ko 12:7…®n gan. N…® akar Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba Jerusalem d…®kab…®razim…®n gans…®va Luk 21:24…®n gan.\f*
\v 3 Eght…® k…® uan akam…®n gun m…®k…®mamin gumazir pumuning amadagh gavgavim aning danight…®ma, aning iz…® nan akam inigh mangam. Aning os…®mt…®zir korotiabar aghuigh…®va, egh nan akam kun mang…®va, 1,260 plan dughiabar tugham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Gumazir kamning mati oliv…®n temer pumuning ko lam…®n pumuning nguazir kam…®n Ekiam…®n guam…®n tughav iti.\f + \ft (11:4) N…® Sekaraia 4:1-5, ko 4:10-14, ko Akar Mogomem 1:12…®n gan.\f*
\v 5 Eght…® gumazitam arazir kurabar aning damus…®, damut…®, avim aning…®n akamning…®n otogh egh aning…®n apaniba, bar men isigh me gas…®ghasigham. Kamagh…®n, gumazir manam arazir kuram…®n aning damus…®, egh an ovegham.
\v 6 Aning gavgavir overiam…®n aneghoroghamim iti, eght…® aning God…®n akam…®n gun m…®geir dughiam…®n, aning m…®k…®mt…®, amozim dughiar kam…®n izan kogham. Eght…® aning gavgavir d…®pabar amut…® da bar ghuzim…®n otivamim iti. Egha uaghan gavgavir nguazim…®n gumazamiziba bizir kurar igharazibar amut…® da me gas…®ghas…®ghamim iti. Dughiar kam…®n, aning bizir kabara amut…® da aning ifongez…® mogh…®n otivam.
\p 
\v 7 Aning God…®n akam…®n gun m…®geir ingangarim g…®vaght…® mozir torir bar konezim…®n itir as…®zir atiam, a torim ategh anangam. Egh an aning ko m…®sogh…®va, egh aning ab…®ragh aning m…®sueght…® aning aremegham.
\v 8 Eght…® aning…®n kuamning nguibar ekiar kam…®n tuavir ekiam…®n ir…®gh…®v ikiam. E akar is…®n zuim…®n a d…®bora ghaze, Sodom o Isip. Nguibar kamra me fom…®ra gumazir kamning…®n Ekiam temem…®n a gafugha a m…®soghez…® an ovenge.
\v 9 Gumazamizir m…®karzir igharagha gariba, men marazi, ko anababar dar gumazamizir maba ko nguibabar akaba bar dar gumazamizir maba ko kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba, men marazi, me dughiar 3 pla ko akuam…®n aning…®n kuamning…®n ganam. Egh aning…®n kuamning mozim daghuan anogoregham.
\v 10 Nguazim…®n gumazamiziba kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kamning nguazim…®n gumazamiziba m…®zazir bar kuram me gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n, me aning…®n ovevem bar a gifuegham, egh bar ighiabar amu, egh dam…®va egh uan namakaba bizir aghuiba me dan…®ngam.
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® 3 plan dughiaba ko dughiar akuar kam g…®vaz…®, God uam aning gamiz…®ma, aning ua d…®kavigha tughav iti, ez…® gumazir aning ganiziba bar atiatingi.
\v 12 Ez…® aning orazi tiarir mam God…®n Nguibam…®n kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua kagh anang.‚Äù Ez…® aning…®n apaniba garav…®ra itima, aning God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanabo.
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® dughiar kamra m…®k…®mk…®zir dafam otoz…®, God nguibar ekiam…®n d…®peniba 10 plan okuruabar tuiragha, okuruar mam bar ikufi. Ez…® 7,000 plan gumazamiziba ariagh…®re, ez…® ariaghrezir puvat…®ziba ikiava bar atiatigha God…®n uan Nguibam…®n itim…®n ziam fe.
\p 
\v 14 Iavzika, ia orakigh! Os…®mt…®zir bar ekiar namba 2, a g…®fa. Ez…® os…®mt…®zir bar ekiar namba 3, an otivasa bar rogh…®ra izi.
\s1 Ensel…®n namba 7 uan s…®gham givi
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® ensel…®n namba 7 uan s…®gham givima, God…®n Nguibam…®n itir darazi tiariba akara ghaze,
\q1 ‚ÄúEn Ekiam ko an Gumazir a Gumazamiziba Ua Me Iniasa M…®sevezim,
\q2 aning dat…®r…®gh…®n nguazir kam gativagha an gari.
\q1 Egh aning atrivim…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù\f + \ft (11:15) Grigh…®n akam…®n, Gumazir God Gumazamiziba Ua Me Iniasa M…®sevezim, me kamagh a d…®bora ghaze, Krais.\f*
\b
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® 24 plan gumazir dapanir God…®n guam…®n uan atrivir dabirabibagh apiaziba, me tevir akuriba ap…®righa uan guaba nguazim m…®suegha God…®n ziam fe.
\v 17 Egha m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® God…®n bar gavgavim itim.
\q2 N…® bar fom…®ra ikia egha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n uaghan iti.
\q2 N…® uan gavgavir ekiam inigha egha dat…®r…®gh…®n atrivim…®n iti.
\q3 Kamagh amiz…®, e n…® m…®nabi.
\q1 
\v 18 Kantrin Igharazibar Gumaziba bar puv…®ram atari,
\q2 ez…® n…®n an…®ngagharim otogha g…®fa.
\q1 God gumazamizir ovengeziba tuis…®ghamin dughiam, otogha g…®fa.
\q2 Kar dughiar n…®n ingangarir gumazir n…®n akam inigha izeziba,
\q3 me uan ivezir aghuim iniamim.
\q2 Gumazamizir n…®n atiatia egha n…®n ziam…®n apengan itiba,
\q3 gumazamizir ziaba itiba ko ziaba puvat…®ziba uakan.
\q2 Eght…® gumazamizir nguazim…®n itir gumazibagh as…®ghas…®ziba,
\q3 God uaghan me gas…®ghas…®gham.‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 19 24plan gumazir dapaniba m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®ma, God…®n D…®penir an nguibam…®n itim kuiaghr…®z…®ma, me garima Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim itir Boksiam God…®n D…®penim…®n aven iti. Ez…® overiam…®n on…®mariba taghtagha tintinibar zuima, n…®g…®nir dafam otoz…®, arariba dagarvasi, ez…® m…®k…®mk…®zim otoz…® amozir of…®zir ekiar dag…®abar m…®n gariba iri.
\c 12
\ms1 Satan uan adarazi ko bar ikufi
\mr (Sapta 12-20)
\s1 Jon gara, amizim ko kuruzir ekiam…®n gari
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® overiam…®n p…®n bizir bar igharagha garim oto. Amizir mam, an aruem…®n angazangarim korotiam…®n m…®n aneru, ez…® iakinim an suemning…®n apengan iti, ez…® dapanir asuar m…®kovezir 12 pla itim, an dapanim…®n iti.
\v 2 Amizir kam navim asegha borim batasava amua m…®zazim isava arai.
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® overiam…®n bizir igharagha garir igharazim oto, maburan kuruzir aghevir mam, a dapanir 7 pla ikia, egha 10 plan komba ikia, egha 7 plan atrivim…®n dapanir asuaba vaghavagha an dapanibar iti.
\v 4 Kuruzir kam overiam…®n itir m…®kovezibar 3 plan okuruabar da tuira, egha okuruar mam pamtem uan ipem…®n dar vigha da makuniz…®ma da iza nguazim gire. Kuruzim ghaze, amizim borim bateght…®ma an anemasa, kamagh…®n kuruzim amizim…®n guam…®n tughav iti.
\v 5 Ez…® amizim otarim bate, otarir God m…®sevezim, a ain…®n aghorir gavgavim…®n suiragh…®va gumazamiziba m…®gh…®v…®ra me gativagham. Ez…® an otarim me zuam…®ra a inigha God…®n atrivir dabirabim…®n anefasava a inigha ghuavanabo.
\v 6 Ez…® amizir kam ara gumaziba puvat…®z…® nagh…®n ghu. Danganir kam God a bagha anek…®ri, eght…® a kagh 1,260 plan dughiabar ik…® akurvazim ini ikiam.
\v 7 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n maburan m…®dorozim God…®n Nguibam…®n p…®n oto. Maikel uan enselba ko kuruzir kam m…®sosi, ez…® kuruzir ekiam uan enselba ko men m…®dorozim ikarvasi.
\v 8 Egha kuruzir kam gavgaviba puvat…®gha egha me God…®n Nguibam…®n uan danganim ataki.
\v 9 Ez…® Maikel…®n enselba kuruzir ekiam akuniz…® a izaghira ir…®. Kar kuruzir fom…®ra itim, me Satan a gar…®si egha uaghan an ziar mam, ‚ÄúGumazir Akam Gumazamizibagh asim.‚Äù A gumazir nguazim…®n itir gumazamizibagh ifarim, a dat…®r…®gh…®n uan enselba ko iza nguazim gir…®.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® k…® God…®n Nguibam…®n tiarir ekiar mam barazi a kamagh…®n m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúGumazir God…®n guam…®n tugha d…®magariba ko aruebar en adarazi akam me gasim,
\q2 me a isa anekuniz…® a ir…®gha nguazim…®n iraghu.
\q1 Kamagh…®n, dat…®r…®gh…®n God uan gumazamizibar akurvasi,
\q2 ez…® an gavgavim bar azenim gir…®z…®,
\q3 A Bizibagh Ativir Dughiam otogha g…®fa!
\q1 Ez…® an Gumazir A Gumazamiziba Uam Me Iniasa M…®sevezim,
\q2 uan gavgavim inigha gumazamizibar akaz…®,
\q3 me an apengan iti!
\q1 
\v 11 Krais…®n adarazi, dughiar gumaziba me m…®sozima me ariagh…®rim,
\q2 dughiar kam…®n me uan m…®karzibagh
\q3 n…®ghn…®zir pu. Puvat…®. Me ghaze, pura bizim.
\q1 Kamagh…®n, me sipsip…®n nguzim…®n ghuzim ko guiz…®n akar me gun m…®geim…®n,
\q2 me Satan…®n m…®suegha aneb…®ra.
\q1 
\v 12 Kamagh amiz…®, ia God…®n Nguibam ko an itir darasi bar,
\q2 ia bar akongegh!
\q1 Ez…® gua nguazim ko ongarim guavzika,
\q2 gua bar ikuvigham.
\q1 Satan fo, a ikiamin dughiam bar otefe,
\q2 kamagh amiz…® a guan an…®ngagh…® gua gas…®ghas…®ghasa gua bagha izaghir…®.
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, guan aven itir darasi,
\q2 Iavzika.‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® kuruzim fo, me anekuniz…® a nguazim…®n iraghu, egha amizir otarim batezir kam…®n ag…®ra.
\v 14 God kamagh sua, amizim azenir 3 pla ko akuam…®n gumaziba puvat…®z…® nagh…®n ik…®va egh a kagh akurvazim iniam. Kamagh…®n, a m…®ghegh danganir God a bagha d…®k…®r…®zir kam…®n mangasa, God kuarazir anebar ekiam…®n av…®zimning a gan…®ngi.
\v 15 Kuruzim kamagh sua, aperiar ekiam amizim inigh mang…®gham. Egha kamagh…®n uan akam…®n d…®par ekiam…®n miki, ez…® d…®par kam aperiar ekiam…®n m…®n ivegha amizim…®n g…®n zui.
\v 16 Ez…® nguazim amizim…®n akurvagha, akam akarigha d…®par kuruzim mighizir kam tui.
\v 17 Kamagh amiz…®, kuruzim amizim puv…®ram an atara ghua an borir igharaziba ko m…®soghasa, me God…®n akabar g…®n zuiba ko Iesus…®n akam…®n gun m…®geiba.
\v 18 Egha kuruzim ongarir dadarim…®n tughav iti.
\c 13
\s1 As…®zir atiar pumuning oto
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® k…® gari, as…®zir atiar mam ongarim…®n otogha anadi. A dapanir 7 pla iti, ez…® kom…®n 10 pla an dapanibar iti. Ez…® 10 plan atrivim…®n dapanir asuaba vaghvagha an 10 plan kombar iti. Ez…® an dapaniba vaghvagha God…®n ziam…®n tiraghtirazir ziaba dar iti.
\v 2 As…®zir atiar k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n garir kam, a kaziar atiar ekiar me kamagh…®n d…®borim lepat, an a m…®n gari. Ez…® an sueba, as…®zir atiar kurar me kamagh…®n d…®borim bea, an an suebar m…®n gari. Egha an akam laion…®n akam…®n m…®n gari. Ez…® as…®zir atiar kam, kuruzim uan gavgavim ko atrivir dabirabim ko bizibagh ativamin gavgavir ekiam, a gan…®ngi.
\v 3 Nan ganganim…®n as…®zir atiar kam…®n dapanir mam, me a b…®raz…® a duam at…®gha atam aremeghai, egha an duam ua ik…®ri. Ez…® nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba bar d…®gavir kuram gamigha as…®zir atiar kam…®n g…®n zui.
\v 4 Gumazamiziba fo, kuruzim uan gavgavim isa as…®zir atiam gan…®ngi, kamagh…®n me kuruzim…®n ziam fe. Egha uaghan as…®zir atiam…®n ziam fa ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazitam as…®zir atiar kam…®n m…®n gavgavim itir puvat…®! Gumazitam a ko m…®soghan kogham!‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 God as…®zir atiam…®n amamangat…®z…®, an akam God gasava egha God…®n ziam…®n tiraghtirazir gavgavim ikia, ghua 42 plan iak…®nibar tu.
\v 6 Egha uan akam…®n God ko God…®n ziam ko God…®n Nguibam, ko an Nguibam…®n itir darazi sara, men tira.
\v 7 Ez…® God an amamangat…®z…®ma, a God…®n gumazamiziba ko m…®dorozim gamua, egha me m…®suegha me ab…®ra. God gavgavir ekiam a gan…®ngi, ez…® an anababa bar dar gumazamiziba, ko m…®karzir igharagha gariba bar, ko vaghvagha nguibabar akabav geir gumazamiziba, ko kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba, a me gativaghamin gavgavim iti.
\v 8 Eght…® nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba as…®zir atiar kam…®n ziam fam. Fom…®ra, nguazir kam t…®ghar otivamin dughiam…®n, God gumazamizir ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim iniamin ziaba ak…®nafarim…®n aven da osiri. Ak…®nafarir kam, kar me fom…®ra m…®soghez…® aremezir sipsip…®n nguzim…®n ak…®nafarim. Eght…® gumazamizir kabara, me as…®zir atiam…®n ziam fan kogham.
\b
\q1 
\v 9 ‚ÄúTina kuarimning iti, an oragh.
\q2 
\v 10 Eght…® God gumazitam kalabus…®n mang…®s…® an amamangat…®ght…®,
\q3 a kalabus…®n mang…®.
\q2 Eght…® God gumazitam m…®dorozir sabam…®n ovengs…® an amamangat…®ght…®,
\q3 a m…®dorozir sabam…®n ovengam.
\q1 Bizir kaba otivt…®ma,
\q2 God…®n gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…® tugh gavgavigh mamagh…®ra ik…®.‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 11 Egha k…® as…®zir atiar igharazir mam…®n garima, a nguazim…®n anagav oto. Egha an dapanim…®n kom…®n pumuning sipsip…®n nguzim…®n kom…®n m…®n gari. Egha kuruzir ekiam m…®gei mogh…®ra m…®gei.
\v 12 Ez…® as…®zir atiar namba 2…®n kam, as…®zir atiar faragha izezim…®n gavgavim…®n biziba bar dagh ami. Egha nguazim ko an itir gumazamizibagh amima, me as…®zir atiar faragha zuim…®n ziam fe. As…®zir atiar kam, faragha duam ikia aremeghasa amua egha duam ua ik…®ri.
\v 13 Ez…® namba 2…®n as…®zir atiar kam, arazarazir ekiar gumazibar navibagh inivamin av…®ribagh ami. Egha an amizir arazir mam kamak…®n, an avim gamiz…® an overiam ategha izaghira gumazibar damazibar nguazim gir…®.
\v 14 Ez…® God as…®zir atiar namba 2…®n amamangat…®z…®, an arazarazir ekiabagh amiz…® da as…®zir atiar faragha zuim…®n guam…®n otifi. Ez…® an amir arazarazir kabar a nguazim…®n itir gumazamizibagh ifara me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa as…®zir atiar faragha zuim…®n marvir guam…®n ingarigh, an ziam f…®.‚Äù As…®zir atiar kam, me m…®dorozir sabam…®n duam a gat…®z…®, ez…® a uam angamra iti.
\v 15 Ez…® God as…®zir atiar namba 2…®n amamangat…®z…® an as…®zir atiar faragha zuim…®n marvir guar kam gamiz…®, an angamra ikia bizibav gei. Kamagh…®n gumazitaba marvir guar kam…®n ziam fan aghuaght…®, a m…®kemeght…® me me m…®sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiram.
\v 16 Ez…® a uaghan gumazamiziba bar uan osizirim men agharir guviba o men guabar ar…®ghasa pamten me gaghori. Me, gumazamizir k…®niba ko gumazamizir ziaba itiba ko, biziba puvat…®ziba ko, bizir av…®riba itiba ko, pura ingangarir gumazamiziba ko gumazitam…®n apengan itir puvat…®zir gumazamiziba, me bar osizirim ini.
\v 17 Kamagh…®n, gumazitam osizirir kam ikian kogh, egh uan biziba amang…® egh uaghan men bizibagh ivezan kogham. Osizirir kam, an as…®zir atiam…®n ziam, o an ziam…®n aven itir mogomer namba.
\v 18 Gumazim God…®n fofozim ik…®va, egh derav…®ra bizir kam g…®fogham. Egh gumazim fofozir aghuim ik…®, egh derav…®ra as…®zir atiam…®n namba tuis…®gh…®va a buriam. Kar gumazir mam…®n ziam…®n namba. An namba kara, 666.\f + \ft (13:18) Me fom…®ra, Hibrun akam ko Grigh…®n akam…®n osira, egha nambaba osirir puvat…®. Me osirir letaba, maba nambabar m…®n iti. Men leta ‚Äòa‚Äô, a mati namba 1, ez…® leta ‚Äòb‚Äô mati namba 2, egha da d…®bora kamagh…®ra zui. Eght…® gumazitam ziatam osirt…®, n…® ziar kam…®n letabar gan, egh namban ababanir an ziam…®n m…®rara zuiba akuvaght…®, an ziam otogham. Ez…® fofozir gumazir maba namban kam 666, me n…®ghn…®zir bar av…®ribar a gami. Egha fofozir gumazir bar av…®rim ghaze, Jon ti Sisar Neron m…®gei. A Rom…®n atrivir mam, a faragha Krais…®n adarazigh as…®ghas…®ki.\f*
\c 14
\s1 Sipsip…®n nguzim…®n gumazamiziba ighiar igiam gami
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® k…® ua gari, sipsip…®n nguzim Sion…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n tughav iti. Ez…® 144,000…®n gumazamiziba a ko tuivighav iti. Ez…® sipsip…®n nguzim…®n ziam ko an afeziam…®n ziam…®n osizirim men guabar iti.
\v 2 Ez…® k…® orazi, tiarir mam God…®n Nguibam…®n m…®gei, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, d…®par ekiaba puv…®ra n…®di mogh…®n n…®ga, egha arariba dagarvazi mogh…®n dagarvasi, gumaziba uan gitabav sozi mogh…®n, pamten m…®gei.
\v 3 Egha 144,000…®n gumazamiziba, me ikia God…®n atrivir dabirabim ko 4 plan bizir angamra itiba ko gumazir dapaniba, me men guam…®n tuivighav ikia ighiar igiar mam gami. Me gumazamizir God ua ivezeziba, merara ighiar igiar kam g…®fo. Eght…® gumazir igharazitam ua ighiar igiar kam g…®foghan kogham.
\v 4 Ez…® gumazamizir 144,000…®n kaba amizitaba isa da ko akua egha arazir kuratam gamigha God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir puvat…®. Me bar zuegha iti. Me sipsip…®n nguzim aruir daroribar gara darara g…®n zui. God nguazim…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n 144,000 plan gumazamizir kabanagh ua me givese. Ez…® me, God ko sipsip…®n nguzim uari bagha faraghav…®ra inabazir gumazamizibara. Eght…® me aning…®n adarazir m…®n ikiam.\f + \ft (14:4) Vez…®n kam, Grigh…®n akam guizbang…®ra ghaze, me gumazamiziba uari ko akuir arazim gamizir puvat…®. Ez…® fofozir gumazir av…®rim ghaze, a gumazamizir derav…®ra God ifongezir arazibar g…®n zuim…®n akar is…®n zuim m…®gei. Me arazir kurar guar av…®ribagh amizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 5 Men akatoribar ifavaritam otozir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazitam akatam me gasir puvat…®.
\s1 Ensel…®n 3 pla akam akuri
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® k…® ensel…®n igharazim…®n garima an overiam…®n p…®n m…®ghegha zui. A nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba bar, gumazamizir kantriba bar dar itiba ko, anababa bar ko, nguibabar akaba bar ko, m…®karzir igharagha gariba bar, me bagha zurara itir akar aghuim akunasa m…®ghegha zui.
\v 7 Egha a pamten kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod gumazamizibar arazibar tuis…®ghamin dughiam bar rogh…®ra ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia God…®n atiating, egh ziar ekiam a dan…®ng. Ia, overiam ko nguazim ko ongarim ko nguazim…®n aven ivemarir d…®pabar ingarizir God, an ziam f…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® ensel…®n an g…®rara irir mam iza ghaze, ‚ÄúBabilon…®n Nguibar Ekiam bar ikufi. Guizbang…®ra a ikuvigha g…®vaz…® gumazitam an itir puvat…®. Babilon…®n Nguibar Ekiar kamra gumazamizibagh amiz…®, me a ko arazir uari bak…®a akuir arazir kurar gavgavibagh ami, mati me wain…®n gavgavim me gan…®ngiz…®, me aneme.‚Äù\f + \ft (14:8) Babilon…®n nguibar ekiam fom…®ra ikuvigha itima, Jon g…®n Akar Mogomem…®n ak…®nafarir kam osiri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, fofozir gumazir av…®rim ghaze, a guizbang…®ra Babilon…®n m…®geir puvat…®. Me ghaze, a Babilon fom…®ra amizir arazir kurabav gei, egh kantrin gavgavir igharaziba, arazibagh amuava egha God…®n apanim gamizibar akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®gei. Ez…® marazi ghaze, a Rom…®n Kantri m…®gei. (N…® 1 Pita sapta 5:13…®n gan.) Ez…® marazi ghaze, ziar kam Babilon, a gumazamizir Krais…®n sios ko an apanim gamiba.\f*
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® ensel…®n m…®kezim aning…®n g…®n iza egha pamten dia ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazitam as…®zir atiar kam ko an marvir guam, aning…®n ziam fa, egha an namba uan guam o agharim…®n a iniva,
\v 10 egh a uaghan wain…®n igharagha garim aneremam. Wain…®n kamnang, a God…®n an…®ngagharim. Eght…® God faragh wain…®n kam d…®patam a gis…®n a ingeght…® an gavgavitaba g…®vaghan kogham. Bar puvat…®. An an…®ngagharir arazim…®n, arazir kuraba ikarvazir itarim gingeght…®ma gumazamizir kaba aneremam. Egha sipsip…®n nguzim…®n damazim ko God…®n enselbar damazim…®n, gumazamizir kaba avim ko salfan dag…®ar avim…®n m…®zazir ekiam iniam.
\v 11 Ez…® avir m…®zazim me gan…®dir kam, an m…®gharim p…®n ghuavanang mamagh…®ra ikiam. Gumazamizir as…®zir atiam ko an marvir guam…®n ziam feba o an namba iniziba, d…®magariba ko aruebar avughsan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Eght…® arazir kaba otivt…®ma, God…®n gumazamiziba tugh gavgafigh. Me gumazamizir God…®n akabar g…®n zuiba ko n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ikiav…®ra itiba.
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® k…® God…®n Nguibam…®n tiarir mam barazi, a kamagh m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® akam kamagh…®n an osirigh. Dat…®r…®gh…®n ik…® mang…®, gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ekiam…®n ikia egh g…®n ovengamiba, me bar akongegh.‚Äù Ez…® God…®n Duam uaghan ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra. Me amir ingangarir os…®mt…®zir kam ategh, egh mang…® avughs…®. Egh me pura mangan kogham. Puvat…®. Arazir aghuir me amiziba men g…®n mang…®t…® God kotiam…®n dar ganam. Kamagh amiz…®, me bar akongegh.‚Äù
\s1 God abuan gumazamiziba tuis…®ghamin dughiam…®n akar is…®n zuim
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® k…® gari, ghuariar ghurghurir mam iti, ez…® gumazir mam gumazibar otarim…®n m…®n gara ghuariar ghurghurir kam gaperaghav iti. Ez…® gol…®n dapanir asuam an dapanim…®n iti, ez…® an dafarim…®n a sabar ik…®z…®r…®zir bar ghumt…®zim…®n suira.\f + \ft (14:14) N…® akar Daniel 7:13…®n itim…®n gan.\f*
\v 15 Ez…® ensel…®n igharazir mam God…®n D…®penim…®n ikegha iza, egha gumazir ghuariar ghurghurim gaperaghav itim, tiarir ekiam…®n an dia ghaze, ‚ÄúNguazim…®n dagheba bar anigha g…®fa, ez…® dagher kaba aghoramin dughiam a dat…®r…®gh…®n oto. Kamagh…®n amiz…® n…® uan sabar ik…®z…®r…®zim inigh, egh daghebar aghor.‚Äù
\v 16 Ez…® gumazir ghuariar ghurghurim gaperazim, uan sabar ik…®z…®r…®zim nguazim…®n a ighengez…®, dagher and…®zir nguazim…®n itiba d…®ghoraghiri.
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® ensel…®n igharazir mam God…®n Nguibam…®n an d…®penim…®n ikegha azenan iza egha uaghan sabar ghumt…®zir mam iti.
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® ensel…®n igharazir mam ofa gamir danganim ategha izi, kar ensel…®n avim…®n garim. Egha a ensel…®n sabar ghumt…®zim…®n suiraghav itim…®n dia ghaze, ‚ÄúWain…®n ov…®ziba anigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® uan sabar ghumt…®zim inigh nguazim…®n wain…®n ov…®ziba kuar egh danganir vam…®ra dar pozim m…®k…®n.‚Äù
\v 19 Ez…® ensel…®n kam uan sabam inigha egha nguazim…®n a ighengez…®ma nguazim…®n wain…®n ov…®ziba bar kuaragh…®re. Ez…® a da isa dar pozim m…®k…®ri, egha da isa dag…®ar m…®ner bar ekiam…®n da akuni. Eght…® me da m…®rm…®ram. Wain…®n ov…®zibar m…®rm…®ramin m…®ner ekiar kam, a God gumazamizibar an…®ngaghamin arazim aka.
\v 20 Ez…® me dag…®ar m…®ner ekiar kam…®n wain…®n ov…®ziba nguibar ekiam…®n azenan da m…®rm…®ri. Ez…® ghuzim dag…®ar m…®nem…®n azenan iza, egha aperiam…®n m…®n ghua 300 kilomitan tu. Ez…® ghuzim…®n konim anaga mitan pumuning…®n borogh…®n tu.\f + \ft (14:20) Fofozir gumazir av…®rim ghaze, nguibar ekiar kam a Jerusalemra. Me Grigh…®n akam…®n namban kam osiri, ‚Äú1,600 stadia,‚Äù ez…® an d…®bobonim, en 300 kilomitan m…®n ghu. E derav…®ra fozir puvat…®, e d…®bori mogh…®n 300 kilomitan namban kam a 1,600…®n d…®bobonim ko aning magh ghuz…®, o kar bizir igharazim…®n ababanim…®n d…®bobonim.\f*
\c 15
\s1 Ensel…®n 7 pla bizir bar kurar 7 plan suiki
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® k…® God…®n Nguibam…®n gari, bizir igharagha garim otifi, ez…® k…® bar d…®gavir kuram gami. K…® 7 plan enselbar gari, me ikia egha 7 plan bizir bar kurar gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®zibar suiki. Eght…® 7 plan bizir kurar kaba g…®vaght…®, ua igharaziba otivan kogham, kamagh amiz…®, bizir kurar 7 plan kabanang…®n g…®n, God…®n an…®ngagharim bar g…®vagham.
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® k…® bizir ekiar mam…®n gari, a mati ongarir ekiam me glas ko avim sarama an ingari. Gumazamiziba faragha as…®zir atiar kam ko an marvir guam, ko an ziam…®n namba, me dav sogha da ab…®ni. Egha me dat…®r…®gh…®n ongarir glas…®n m…®n garir kam…®n m…®riam…®n tuivighav ikia, egha God me gan…®ngiz…®r gitabar suiki.\f + \ft (15:2) Saptan kam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®rim, da Moses osirizir eghaghaniba ko magh ghue. Moses Isip bagha as…®ghas…®ghasa an…®ngagharim gamiz…® an oto. Israelba ongarim a bigha Isipba ategha vong…®n ongarir dadarim…®n tuivaghav…®ra ikia, egha Moses Israelba ko me ighiar mam gamua egha ekiam…®n ziam fe. (N…® Kisim Bek 15…®n gan.)\f*
\v 3 Egha me God…®n ingangarir gumazim, Moses ko sipsip…®n nguzim, me aning…®n ighiam gamua kamagh…®n m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúEkiam God, n…® gavgaviba bar iti!
\q2 N…® arazarazir igharagha garir ekiabagh ami,
\q3 ez…® e dar gara egha d…®gavir kurabagh ami!
\q1 N…® gumazamiziba bar men atrivim!
\q2 N…®n araziba, da bar deragha egha bar guizbang…®ra!
\q1 
\v 4 Ekiam n…® uab…®ra guizbang…®ra God.
\q2 Eght…® gumazamiziba bar n…®n atiatigh egh ziar ekiam n…® dan…®ng.
\q1 N…®n arazir aghuiba bar azenim gir…®gha g…®fa,
\q2 kamagh…®n amiz…® kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba bar iz…®
\q3 n…® bagh teviba ap…®r n…®n ziam fam.‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® bizir kam…®n g…®n k…® ua gari, God…®n D…®penim, a God…®n Nguibam…®n Averpenim, a kuiaghir…®. Kar God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim aven itir Averpenim.\f + \ft (15:5) M…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam a Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim…®n gun m…®gei. God…®n Akar Gavgavir D…®k…®r…®zim…®n Boksiam, a Bar Anogoroghezir Danganim…®n aven ikia, egha God…®n Averpenim…®n aven iti.\f*
\v 6 Ez…® ensel…®n 7 plan kaba, bizir bar kurar 7 plan gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®ghamibar suigha God…®n D…®penim ategha azenan izi. Me inir igiar bar zuruzir dafoziba da ike. Egha gol…®n letiaba uan evariba kuamigha da ike.
\v 7 Ez…® 4 plan bizir angamra itibar mav, 7 plan gol…®n itariba inigha ensel…®n 7 pla gan…®ngi. Gol…®n itarir 7 plan kabanagh, zurara itir God…®n an…®ngagharir arazim, dagh iz…®fa.
\v 8 Ez…® God…®n D…®penim, an angazangarim ko an gavgavim…®n m…®gharim, bar a giz…®fa. Kamagh…®n gumazitam d…®penim…®n aven mangan kogham. Kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® 7 plan enselba, 7 plan bizir bar kurar gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®ghamin ingangarim g…®vagham.
\c 16
\s1 Enselba God…®n an…®ngagharir 7 plan itaribar itiba nguazim ginge
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® k…® tiarir ekiar mam barazi, a God…®n D…®penim…®n otogha kamagh…®n 7 plan enselbav gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…®, God…®n an…®ngagharir arazir 7 plan itaribar itiba inigh mang…® nguazim…®n da ing…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® namba 1 ensel uan itarir God…®n an…®ngagharim iz…®vazim inigha ghua nguazim…®n a inge, ez…® duar bar igharagha garir kurar gavgaviba, gumazamizir as…®zir atiam…®n namba itiba ko an marvir guam…®n ziam febar, men m…®karzibar otifi.
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® namba 2 ensel uan itarim ongarim…®n a inge, ez…® ongarim…®n d…®pam gumazir aremezir kuam…®n ghuzim…®n m…®n oto. Ez…® bizir angamra an itiba, da bar ariagh…®re.
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® namba 3 ensel uan itarim faner d…®paba ko d…®par atuibagh inge. Ez…® d…®par kaba bar mogh…®ra ghuzim…®n m…®n oto.
\v 5 Ez…® k…® orazi, ensel…®n d…®pabar garim kamagh…®n m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúGod, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ikia, egha uaghan faragha ike.
\q2 N…® bar guizbang…®ra God.
\q3 N…®n araziba bar deraz…® arazir kuratam n…®n itir puvat…®.
\q1 N…® gumazamizibar arazir kuraba da tuis…®gha
\q2 da ikarvagha ivezir kuram me gan…®ngi,
\q3 ez…® n…®n arazir kam a guiz…®n arazim.
\q1 
\v 6 Gumazir kaba n…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba ko n…®n gumazamizibav soghez…®
\q2 men ghuziba irez…® me ariagh…®re.
\q1 Ez…® n…® ghuzim gumazir kurar kabagh an…®ngiz…®,
\q2 eght…® me aneremam.
\q3 Ghuzir me apir kam, men arazir kurar me amiziba ikarvagham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® k…® orazi tiarir mam God…®n ofa gamir danganim…®n aven otogha pamten diagha ghaze,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúEkiam, n…® God…®n bar gavgavim itim.
\q2 N…® gumazamizibar araziba kot…®n bar guizbang…®ra da tuis…®si,
\q3 ez…® n…®n kotiam a bar guizbang…®ra ghua egha bar dera.‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® namba 4 ensel uan itarim aruem ginge, ez…® God aruem an amamangat…®z…® an avim pamten isia puv…®ra gumazamizibar isi.
\v 9 Aruem…®n avir gavgavir kam bar puv…®ra isia, egha gumazir kabar m…®karziba puv…®ra men isi. Ez…® me bar puv…®ra God…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®gha a m…®gei, kar bizir kurar kabar garir God…®n gavgavim itim. Egha me uan navibagh iragha an ziam fer puvat…®.
\p 
\v 10-11 Ez…® ensel…®n namba 5 uan itarim as…®zir atiam…®n atrivir dabirabim ginge. Ez…® m…®tatem gumazamizir an gavgavim…®n apengan itiba avara. Ez…® me uan duaba ko m…®zazir men m…®karzibar otiviba bagha n…®ghn…®gha, God…®n uan Nguibam…®n itim…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®gha a m…®gei. Ez…® m…®zazir me isim a bar men ikufi, kamagh…®n me uan m…®zebagh ivi. Egha me uan arazir kurar me amiba bagha uan navibagh irazir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® ensel…®n namba 6 uan itarim Yufretis…®n faner ekiam ginge. Ez…® an d…®pam bar mogh…®ra dake, egha aruem anadi nagh…®n atrivir izamiba bagha tuavim at…®.
\v 13 Ez…® k…® gari, duar kurar 3 plan m…®tivibar m…®n gariba, da as…®zir atiam ko, kuruzir ekiam ko akar ifavaribagh amir gumazim…®n, da vaghvagha men akatoribar otifi.\f + \ft (16:13) Akar ifavarim akurir gumazim an as…®zir atiar namba 2…®n ababanim. A faragha itir as…®zir atiam…®n akar ifavarim akurir gumazim. A gumazamizibav geima, me as…®zir faragh itim…®n marvir guam…®n ziam fe.\f*
\v 14 Duar bar kurar kaba arazarazir igharagha garibagh ami da otifi, egha nguazim…®n itir kantriba bar dar atriviba bagha, tintinibar zui. Me atrivibar amut…® me uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigh iz…® me akuvasa. Eght…® God…®n Gavgaviba Bar Itim gumazamiziba tuis…®ghamin dughiar ekiam…®n, me m…®dorozim damuam.
\b
\pm 
\v 15 ‚ÄúIa orakigh! K…®, ok…®mak…®ar gumazim…®n m…®n izam, a izir dughiam ia a g…®fozir puvat…®zir mogh…®n, k…® zuam…®ra otogham. Kamagh amiz…®, gumazim akuir puvat…®gha, egha uan korotiaba uab…®n borogh…®n da ar…®si, egh a bibiamra daruan kogham, eght…® gumazamiziba an gant…®, an aghums…®ghan kogham. Kamagh…®n, gumazir kam bar akongegh.‚Äù\f + \ft (16:15) Ves 15…®n kam, kar Krais Iesus uab…® m…®kemezir akam.\f*
\b
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® duar kuraba atriviba inigha iza danganir kam…®n me akufa, me Hibrun akam…®n kamagh danganir kam d…®bori, Armagedon.\f + \ft (16:16) Ziar kam Armagedon kamak…®n, ‚ÄúMegidon…®n M…®ghs…®am.‚Äù Fom…®ra apaniba Israelba ko uariv sogha egha atrivim Josuan m…®soghez…® an areme. Me Megidon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®ra. (N…® 2 King 23:29-30 ko 2 Stori 35:20-21…®n gan.) Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ziar kam Megido bighav…®ra m…®geir puvat…®. Me ghaze, an akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba mangamin danganim m…®gei. Egh me mang…® bar ikuvigh egh bar ovengam.\f*
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® namba 7 ensel uan itarim overiam…®n a inge. Ez…® God…®n D…®penim…®n aven tiarir ekiar mam God…®n atrivir dabirabim…®n otogha egha kamagh…®n pamten m…®gei, ‚ÄúBiziba bar g…®fa.‚Äù
\v 18 Ez…® overiam…®n on…®mariba taghtagha zuima, n…®g…®nir dafam overiam…®n otoz…®, arariba dagarvasi, ez…® m…®k…®mk…®zir ekiam oto. Kar m…®k…®mk…®zir bar ekiam, fom…®ra gumazamiziba otozir dughiam…®n iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tu, m…®k…®mk…®zir ekiar katam fom…®ra otozir puvat…®.
\v 19 Ez…® Babilon…®n nguibar ekiam b…®aghregha 3 plan okuruabar otifi, ez…® gumazibar nguibaba bar mogh…®ra ikufi. God Babilon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n arazir kuram g…®n…®ghn…®gha, egha a gamiz…® a uan wain…®n itarim bar aneme, kar God…®n an…®ngagharir arazim…®n wain…®n itarim.
\v 20 Ez…® arighat…®ziba bar arav ghue, ez…® m…®ghs…®atam ua itir puvat…®.
\v 21 Ez…® maburan amozir of…®ziba dag…®abar m…®n izaghiri. Ez…® amozir of…®zir dag…®ar kaba vaghvagha, dar os…®mt…®ziba 50 kilogram…®n iti. Amozir dag…®ar kaba overiam…®n izaghira gumazamizibagh is…®n ira bar me gas…®ghas…®si. Bizir kurar kam bagha me God…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®gha m…®gei.
\c 17
\s1 Arazir kurabagh amir amizim ivezir kuram isi
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® 7 plan ensel…®n itarir 7 plan suighizir kabanagh…®n mav iza kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® kagh iz…®. Eght…® k…® amizir ivezir kuram iniamim, n…®n akakaghasa. Amizir kam, arazir kurabagh amir amizim, a d…®par av…®ribagh is…®n aperaghav itir amizim, a nguibar bar ekiar me d…®par av…®ribar m…®riabar ingarizim.
\v 2 Nguazim…®n atriviba arazir m…®z…®r…®zir bar kurar av…®riba amizir kam ko dagh ami. Ez…® nguazim…®n gumazamiziba uaghan a ko arazir bar m…®z…®r…®zibagh amua, egha gumazim wain…®n av…®rim amez…® mogh…®n ongani.‚Äù\f + \ft (17:2) Gumazamiziba arazir bar m…®z…®r…®zibagh amir arazir kam…®n akam, a gumazir God ataghizir arazim…®n ababanim, egha God…®n ifavariba ko arazir kurar igharazibar g…®n zui. Egha God…®n damazim…®n, a mati gumazim uab…® uan amuim ategha, ghua gumazamiziba uari isava akua amir arazim gami.\f*
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® God…®n Duam pamtem nan ingarima, k…® irebam…®n m…®n bizim…®n gari, ensel na inigha gumaziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghu. Ez…® danganir kam…®n k…® amizir mam…®n garima an as…®zir atiar aghevir mam gis…®n aperaghav iti. As…®zir atiar kam…®n m…®karzim osizirir av…®riba an iti, ez…® osizirir kabanagh God…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®si. As…®zir atiar kam 7 pla dapaniba iti, ez…® 10 pla komba an dapanibar iti.
\v 4 Amizir kam korotiar aghuibarama aghui, dar ganganim aghevim ko p…®ghaghevim. Ez…® gol…®n d…®g…®rir bar aghuiba ko, me dag…®ar aghuibar ingarizir d…®g…®riba ko, manmaniar ghurghurir dag…®aba p…®n koziba, amizir kam…®n m…®karzim giz…®fa. Egha a uan dafarim…®n gol…®n itarir mam suiraz…®, itarir kam…®n aven bar kurigha mughazir araziba ko, gumazamiziba tintinibar uari bak…®a amir arazir bar m…®z…®r…®zir kuraba, a giz…®fa.
\v 5 Ez…® amizir kam…®n guam…®n me ziar mam osiri, ziar kam…®n m…®ngarim modoghav iti. Ez…® an m…®ngarim kamak…®n,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúBabilon…®n nguibar ekiar gavgavim itim,
\q2 n…® nguazim…®n itir arazir bar kuraba ko amizir gumaziba ok…®a me ko akua arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh amiba,
\q3 n…® men amebam.‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® k…® gari, amizir kam God…®n gumazamizibar ghuziba amegha d…®par onganiba amez…® mogh…®n ongani. Gumazamizir kaba, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n ikia an akam akuri, ez…® me me m…®soghez…® me ariagh…®re.
\p K…® amizir kam…®n ganigha d…®gavir kuram gamigha pura n…®ghn…®si.
\v 7 Ez…® ensel kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha d…®gavir kuram gami? Amizir kam ko as…®zir atiar anetera zuim, a 7 plan dapaniba ko 10 plan komba an iti, aning…®n akar mogomem…®n m…®ngarim, k…® n…®n akagham.
\v 8 As…®zir atiar n…® faragha ganizir kam, a faragha ike, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n ua itir puvat…®. Egh mozir bar konezim ategh azenan iz…®t…®, God a gas…®ghas…®gham. God t…®ghar nguazim…®n ingaramin dughiam, a gumazamizir maba men ziaba ak…®nafarir zurara itim…®n aven da osirizir puvat…®. Gumazamizir kaba as…®zir atiar kam…®n ganigh d…®gavir kuram damuam. Me fo, a fom…®ra ike, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n itir puvat…®, egh a g…®n uamategh otivam.
\p 
\v 9 ‚ÄúGumazim God…®n fofozir aghuim ik…®va, egh bizir kam deragh a g…®fogham. 7 plan dapanir kaba, kar m…®ghs…®ar 7 pla, ez…® amizim 7 plan m…®ghs…®abagh is…®n aperaghav iti.\f + \ft (17:9) Gumaziba Rom…®n nguibar ekiam, 7 plan m…®ghs…®abagh is…®n an ingari.\f*
\v 10 Egha ada uaghan 7 plan atrivibar ababanim gami. 5 pla ariaghregha g…®fa, ez…® vam…®ra atrivim…®n ikiav…®ra iti, ez…® igharazir abuananam t…®ghar otivam; an otogh…®va bar dughiar otevimra ikiam.
\v 11 As…®zir atiar kam, a fom…®ra ike, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n itir puvat…®, a namba 8 atrivim…®n ababanim. Egha a 7 plan atrivibar mav, God a gas…®ghasight…® a bar g…®vagham.
\p 
\v 12 ‚ÄúEz…® 10 plan kom…®n n…® ganiziba da 10 plan atrivibar ababaniba. Me t…®ghar atrivibar otivam. Me bizibagh ativamin gavgavim inigh, as…®zir atiar kam ko dughiar bar otevimrama atrivibar ikegham.
\v 13 Atrivir kaba n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra ikiam, egh uan gavgaviba ko ziar ekiaba is…® as…®zir atiamra dan…®ngam.
\v 14 Egh me m…®dorozim sipsip…®n nguzim koma a damuam, eght…® sipsip…®n nguzim me gas…®ghas…®gh me ab…®ragham. Gumazir sipsip…®n nguzim ko itiba, God me am…®sevegha, egha men diaz…®ma me guiz…®n akam…®n g…®n ghua tuivigha gavgavigha m…®dorozir kam gami. Sipsip…®n nguzim, a guizbang…®ra Gumazir Ekiabar Gumazir Ekiam ko Atrivibar Atrivir Ekiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…® a me ab…®ragham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® ensel kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúD…®par n…® ganizir kabanang, amizir arazir kurabagh amim dagh is…®n aperaghav iti, dar m…®ngarimra kara: ada m…®karzir igharagha gariba ko, dakoziba bar dar gumazamiziba ko, kantriba bar dar gumazamiziba ko, vaghvagha akabav geir gumazamiziba.
\v 16 As…®zir atiam ko 10 pla kom…®n n…® ganizir kabanang, arazir kurabagh amir amizim…®n apanim damuam. Me an biziba bar da inigh egh an korotiaba bar da suegh, egh me an m…®karzim…®n tuziba bar dar amegh, egh avim…®n a daboroght…®ma a bar mogh…®ra isigham.
\v 17 God uab…® me gan…®ngizir n…®ghn…®zir kam, a me damut…® biziba otivam. Kamagh…®n me n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra ik…®, egh atrivim…®n ikiamin gavgaviba bar da is…® as…®zir atiam dan…®ngam. Me kamagh…®n damu mang…®t…® God…®n akam m…®kemezir biziba, da guiz…®n otivamin dughiam otogham.
\v 18 Ez…® amizir n…® ganizim, a nguazir kam…®n atriviba bar dar garir nguibar ekiam…®n ababanim.‚Äù
\c 18
\s1 Babilon bar mogh…®ra ikufi
\p 
\v 1 Bizir kam…®n g…®n k…® ensel…®n igharazim…®n garima a God…®n Nguibam ategha izaghiri. A bar gavgavir ekiam iti, ez…® an angazangarir gavgavim nguazim bar a gisira.
\v 2 A pamten diagha kamagh…®n m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúBabilon…®n nguibar ekiam ikuvigha g…®fa! A ikufi!
\q2 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n duar kuraba ko adariar m…®z…®r…®zir kuraba ko kuarazir m…®z…®r…®ziba ko kuarazir kuraba, darara an iti.
\q1 
\v 3 Nguazim…®n nguibaba bar, me an wain…®n itarim uari ok…®a akuava amir arazir kuraba iz…®vazim aneme.
\q2 Ez…® nguazim…®n atriviba a ko arazir m…®z…®r…®zir bar kurabagh ami.
\q2 Ez…® biziba amaga dagh ivezir gumaziba, me an afiar arazir bar ikuvt…®zibar amodogh…®n dag…®ar av…®riba uari bagha da isi.
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, amizir kam bar ikufi.‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® k…® tiarir igharazir mam God…®n Nguibam…®n a barazi, a kamagh…®n m…®gei,
\q1 ‚ÄúIa nan gumazamiziba, ia nguibar kam ategh azenan iz…®.
\q2 Egh an amir arazir kuraba uaghan dar amuan mark…®.
\q1 God an arazir kurabar ikarvaghamin dughiam,
\q2 ia uaghan an aven ikian mark…®!
\q1 
\v 5 A uab…® uan arazir kurabar pozim m…®k…®rav iti,
\q2 da ghuavanaga God…®n Nguibam…®n oto.
\q3 Ez…® God an amizir arazir kurabagh n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti.
\q1 
\v 6 Egh ia amizir kam gumazamizibagh amizir arazir kuraba bagh ivezir magh garimra a ikaragh.
\q2 An arazir kuraba, da bar av…®raseme,
\q3 kamagh…®ra ia an arazir kurabar ivezim a isafuragh…®va bar a dan…®ngigh.
\q2 Egh d…®par onganir gavgavim…®n itarim isa a gumazamiziba bagha a ingegh,
\q3 kamagh…®ra ia d…®par gavgavir onganim uam a isafuragh a bagh itarim ginegh a dan…®ngigh.
\q1 
\v 7 A uab…®ra kamagh uab…®n m…®g…®a ghaze,
\q2 ‚ÄòK…® atrivir amizim, egha atrivir dabirabim gaperaghav iti.
\q2 K…® amizir odiarim…®n m…®n itir puvat…®,
\q2 eght…® os…®mt…®ziba na bativan koght…®, k…® azian kogham!‚Äô
\q1 A uab…® uan ziar gavgavim fa egha arazir m…®z…®r…®zir av…®ribagh amua,
\q2 egha arazir kurar igharaziba saram ami.
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia m…®zazir kurar ekiam ko os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam a dan…®ngigh,
\q2 mang…® an amir arazibar ikegh mang…® tuz…® naghram, a dan…®ng.
\q1 
\v 8 Amizir kam Babilon, uan ziar gavgavim kamagh…®n a fe,
\q2 kamagh…®n amiz…® dughiar bar otevir vam…®ran, bizir bar kuraba bar a bativam.
\q1 Bizir kaba, ar…®mariar ekiaba ko os…®mt…®zir ekiaba a bativt…®
\q2 an azit…®ma, m…®tiriar ekiaba an agham.
\q1 Eght…® avim an isigham.
\q2 Ekiam God an araziba tuis…®gha g…®vagha ghaze,
\q3 ‚ÄòA ikuvigham.‚Äô
\q1 God…®n kam gavgavir ekiam iti.
\q2 Kamagh amiz…®, bizir ikurar av…®riba dughiar vam…®ra bar mogh…®ram a bativam.‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 9 ‚ÄúNguazim…®n atriviba a ko arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh amua, egha uaghan a ko arazir ikurar igharagha garibagh ami. Eght…® atrivir kabanagh an gant…® avir m…®gharim an otoght…®ma, me a bagh naviba osemegh egh a bagh aziam.
\v 10 Egha me m…®zazir ekiar a isir kam…®n ganigh, egh atiatigh saghon tuivigh ik…®, kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam,
\q1 ‚ÄòNoka, Babilon noka,
\q2 n…® nguibar ekiar gavgavim itim!
\q1 N…®n arazir kurabar ivezir kuram dughiar otevimra
\q2 n…® bagha ize.‚Äô
\b
\p 
\v 11 ‚ÄúEght…® biziba amaga dagh ivezir gumazir nguazim…®n itiba, me Babilon g…®n…®ghn…®gh egh a bagh aziva, egh naviba bar osemegham. Me gari, gumazir men dag…®aba bagh amadir bizibagh ivezamiba ua itir puvat…®, kamagh…®n me oseme.
\v 12 Me dag…®aba bagha amadir bizibar kara, gol ko silva ko, dag…®ar aghuiba ko manmaniar iveziba bar p…®n koziba; ko inir ghurghurir aghuiba ko inir p…®ghaghevir aghuiba ko inir slika ko inir agheviba, ko men temer mughuriar aghuir igharagha gariba ko bizir me elefan…®n ataribar ingariziba ko, bizir me temer iveziba bar p…®n itibar ingariziba ko, bras ko ain ko, dag…®ar aghuir d…®g…®riba itiba.
\v 13 Bizir me amaga dag…®aba isir igharaziba uaghan iti, adar kara, sinamon ko, apir iriziba ko, pauran m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim gamim ko, gris…®n igharagha garir mughuriar aghuim zuiba ko, sandan aghuim ko, wain ko, wel ko, plauan aghuim ko witba; men bulmakauba ko, sipsipba ko hoziaba ko dar karisba ko, pura ingangarir gumazir k…®niba‚Äîme dag…®aba bagha men ik…®r…®m…®riba amadi. Bizir kaba bar, gumazir dagh ivezamiba puvat…®.
\p 
\v 14 ‚ÄúGumazir biziba amaga dagh ivezir kaba kamagh…®n a m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòBizir aghuir n…® iniasa navim d…®kavim, dat…®r…®gh…®n da bar n…®n saghuiam…®n ikiam. Bizir bar aghuir av…®rir iveziba bar p…®n koziba ko n…® as…®ngizir bizir ganganir aghuiba, da bar ovengeght…® n…® ua dar ganan kogham!‚Äô
\v 15 Eght…® gumazir nguibar ekiar kam…®n uan bizir kaba amaga dag…®ar av…®riba isiba, tuivigh a isir m…®zazir ekiar kam…®n ganam. Egh bar atiatigh azi, naviba bar osemegh saghon tuivigh, egh kamagh m…®k…®mam,
\b
\q1 
\v 16 ‚ÄòNoka, Babilon…®n nguibar ekiam. Noka!
\q1 A fom…®ra korotiar ghurghurir aghuiba ko inir p…®ghagheviba ko inir aghevir aghuiba aghua,
\q1 egha uan m…®karzim golba ko dag…®ar aghuiba ko manmaniar bar p…®n kozibar aned…®i!
\q1 
\v 17 Ez…® dag…®aba ko dirir aghuir an itir kaba dughiar bar otevimra bar ikufi!‚Äô
\b
\p ‚ÄúEght…® kuribar keptenba ko, gumazir kuribagh arua nguibar igharazibagh aruiba ko, kuribar ingangarir gumaziba ko gumazir ongarim…®n dag…®ar ingangaribagh amiba, me bar mogh…®ra uaghan Babilon…®n saghon tuivigh ikiam.
\v 18 Eght…® Babilon isit…® an m…®gharim otivt…®ma me an gan egh, kamagh…®n diagh m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòNguibar dat…®r…®gh…®n itir manamra, nguibar ekiar kam…®n m…®n gari? Bar puvat…®!‚Äô
\v 19 Egh me uan os…®mt…®zim akaghasa nguazir m…®nem…®niaba inigh uan dapanibagh is…®n da kun, egh naviba bar osemegh egh aziva, egh kamagh…®n d…®m m…®k…®mam,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄòNoka, Babilon…®n nguibar ekiam, noka!
\q2 Ongarim garuir kuribar afeziaba, me nguibar ekiar kam…®n dag…®abar, dag…®ar gumazir ekiabar otifi.
\q3 Mevzika! A dughiar otevimrama bar ikufi!‚Äô
\q1 
\v 20 ‚ÄòIa God…®n Nguibam…®n itir darasi, ia bar akongegh!
\q2 Eght…® ia God…®n gumazamiziba ko aposelba ko God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba,
\q3 ia bar akongegh!
\q1 Arazir kurar nguibar kam ia gamizim baghava,
\q2 God a tuis…®gha g…®vagha, egha uam an arazir kuram ikarvasi.
\q1 Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia dat…®r…®gh…®n nguibar kam batozir bizim bagh bar akongegh.‚Äô‚Äù
\b
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba g…®vaz…®ma, ensel…®n gavgavir mam wit m…®rm…®rir dag…®am…®n m…®n garir dag…®ar ekiam ini. Egha dag…®ar kam fegha a isa ongarim…®n anekunigha egha kamagh…®n m…®gei,
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra, me Babilon…®n nguibar ekiam inigh zuam…®ra pamtem anekunight…®
\q2 a bar mag…®r…®gh bar ikuvight…®,
\q3 eght…® me uam a ganan kogham.
\q1 
\v 22 O Babilon!
\q2 Gitan arareba ko marvibar arareba ko, s…®ghaba ko, ararer aghuir igharazir maba ua n…®n aven otivan kogham.
\q2 Eght…® fofozir gumazir ingangarir guar igharagha garibagh amiba, me ua n…®n ikian kogham!
\q2 Eght…® dag…®ar witba m…®rm…®rim…®n ararem ua n…®n aven otivan kogham!
\q2 
\v 23 Eght…® lam…®n angazangariba ua n…®n aven isian kogham.
\q2 Eght…® gumazamizir uarir ikiasa m…®geir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, da ua n…®n aven otivan kogham.
\q1 N…®n gumazir fom…®ra dag…®aba bagha biziba amadiba, gumazamizir igharazibar damatuzibar gumazir bar ekiabar otifis.
